Name: BMW M Motorsport Electron E Pro Sneakers
descriptions:
Motorsport enthusiasts, meet your new favorite kicks. With a shock-absorbing heel plug-in and SoftFoam+ sockliner, every step feels like a victory lap. The blend of mesh and synthetic leather upper, combined with an EVA midsole, brings BMW MMS' DNA to your daily adventures. Step into the fast lane and live your motorsport passion with PUMA!
SoftFoam+: PUMA’s comfort sockliner for instant step-in and long-lasting comfort that provides soft cushioning every step of your day
Low boot
Heel type: Flat
Shoe width: Regular fit
Shoe pronation: Neutral
Textile upper
Zoned Rubber outsole
Shock-absorbing technology heel plug-in
BMW Motorsport branding
PUMA cat logo branding
Lace fastening

Additional Information:
- Style:308960_03
- Color:PUMA White-Pop Red

Name: CA Pro Classic Leather Sneakers
descriptions:
Elevate your street-style game with these heritage-inspired leather sneakers. Crafted for the modern classic enthusiast, these shoes feature a premium leather upper that combines durability with a polished look. The debossed and foil-printed PUMA branding adds a touch of elegance, while the rubber and TPU pods on the midsole ensure stability and comfort. Perfect for casual outings or elevating your everyday wardrobe, these sneakers are a versatile addition to your collection.
Premium Leather : Durable and stylish, the Upper leather construction offers a sleek, polished look.
Retro Branding: Debossed and foil-printed PUMA logos on the quarter and heel add a classic touch.
All-Day Comfort & Breathability: A cushioned midsole with rubber and TPU pods provides lightweight support, while the mesh lining and PUMA-logo screenprinted sockliner keep your feet cool and comfortable.
Upper: Leather
Ideal For: Casual Outings, Everyday Wear, Urban Exploration
Collection: CA Pro Classic

Additional Information:
- Style:402538_10
- Color:Puma White-Puma Black

Name: Galaxis Pro Mens Performance Boost Running Shoes
descriptions:
These running shoes are the perfect blend of comfort and support. Crafted from superior textile for a lightweight feel, these shoes are built for the long haul. The rounded toe and flat heel offer a seamless stride on the track while the lace-up fastening provides a secure fit. Striking the perfect balance between functionality and style, these shoes keep you in vogue even when you're on the move.
PROFOAM: Offers superior cushioning for all out comfort, supporting you throughout your running journey.
PROTREAD Outsole: Boasts a durable outsole rubber and tread pattern, providing multi-surface traction to keep you steady on your feet.
RUN PUMA Last: A performance fit designed to adapt to your foot's natural movement for a smooth and efficient run.
Fabrics Type: Textile
Shoe Width: Regular
Heel Type: Flat
Surface: Road
Toe Type: Rounded
Built for running distance of up to 500km

- Color:Lime Sheen-PUMA Black-PUMA White

Name: FUEGO Profoam Mens Responsive Cushioned Running Shoes
descriptions:
Stay ahead of the game with these high-performance running shoes, designed for both speed and comfort. Featuring NRGY beads for instant cushioning and IGNITE foam for superior responsiveness, these shoes deliver energy return with every stride. The lightweight textile upper ensures breathability, while the secure lace-up fit provides stability on road surfaces. Whether you're training or running for fun, these shoes combine cutting-edge technology with street-style aesthetics.
NRGY Beads Cushioning: Provides instant comfort and shock absorption.
IGNITE Foam Midsole: Offers excellent responsiveness and energy return.
Lightweight Design: Enhances speed and agility.
Regular Fit with Laces: Ensures a secure and snug fit.
Main Material: Textile
Heel-to-Toe Drop: 12mm (25mm heel, 13mm toe)
Surface: Road Running
Average Lifespan: 800 km

Name: Deviate NITRO Elite 3 Mens Running Shoes
descriptions:
The Deviate NITRO™ Elite 3
running shoes
is built for runners chasing their fastest finish. Its powerful carbon plate and high-energy foam keep you flying through every stride. On race day, it's not just a shoe, it’s your speed weapon. The feather-light ULTRAWEAVE upper keeps you cool and locked in mile after mile.
NITROFOAM™ ELITE: Premium performance foam technology that provides pinnacle responsiveness in an extremely lightweight package
PWRPLATE: Carbon fibre plate engineered to stabilise the midsole while maximising energy transfer
